## Proposed Changes

### Student Attendance Dashboard

#### [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/(student)/student/attendance/page.tsx)

Complete rewrite of the student attendance page. Current page is a plain table. New page:

**Layout (top → bottom, mobile-first):**

1. **Hero Percentage Ring** — Large animated circular progress showing overall %. Color-coded:
   - ≥90% → green
   - ≥75% → amber
   - <75% → red with warning pulse

2. **Summary Strip** — Horizontal row: Present / Absent / Late / Excused counts as small pills

3. **Self-Mark Banner** (conditional) — If any attendance session is currently open for self-marking, show a prominent CTA: "📍 Mark your attendance — closes in 12:34". Tapping calls `POST /api/student/attendance/self-mark`

4. **Calendar Month Grid** — 7-column grid (Mon–Sun), each day cell shows:
   - 🟢 dot if all classes present
   - 🔴 dot if any absent
   - 🟡 dot if late
   - ⚪ if no class that day
   - Tapping a day expands a detail card below the row showing each class (subject, teacher, status)
   - Month navigation arrows (← Feb 2026 →)

5. **Recent Records List** — Below calendar, last 10 records in a compact timeline format (fallback for clarity)

**Animations:**
- Calendar cells fade-in staggered on load (framer-motion)
- Percentage ring animates from 0 → actual on mount
- Self-mark banner has a gentle pulse

---

#### [NEW] [route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/student/attendance/self-mark/route.ts)

[POST](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/auth/register/route.ts#20-169) — Student self-marks present for a specific attendance session.

- Validates: session exists, `self_mark_open === true`, `self_mark_deadline > now`, student is in the batch
- Sets `records[].status = 'present'` and `records[].marked_by = 'self'`
- Returns success/error

---

#### [MODIFY] [route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/student/attendance/route.ts)

Add to the response:
- `open_sessions[]` — Any attendance docs where `self_mark_open === true` and `self_mark_deadline > now` for this student's batch
- `calendar_data` — Records grouped by date for calendar rendering

---

### Teacher Attendance Dashboard

#### [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/(teacher)/teacher/attendance/page.tsx)

Add a **"Today's Sessions" card** at the top showing:
- Active sessions with live counters (X/Y marked)
- Status badges: 🟢 Open, 🟡 Reviewing, ⬜ Finalized
- Quick-resume button for sessions in progress

Below the today card, the existing class list remains.

---

#### [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/(teacher)/teacher/attendance/[classId]/page.tsx)

Add session lifecycle controls to the existing marking page:

1. **Session States:**
   - [open](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/layout/PublicNavbar.tsx#214-218) — Teacher is actively marking. Shows student list with status toggles
   - `reviewing` — Self-mark closed. Teacher reviews and fills gaps (unmarked students default to absent)
   - `finalized` — Locked. Read-only view

2. **Self-Mark Toggle:** A switch in the header: "Allow student self-marking". When toggled ON:
   - Sets `self_mark_open = true` on the attendance doc
   - Shows a configurable timer (default 30 min)
   - Students in the batch see the self-mark banner
   - Live counter updates as students mark themselves

3. **Finalize Button:** Replaces "Save Attendance". When clicked:
   - Sets `status = 'finalized'` and `is_locked = true`
   - Unmarked students auto-set to absent
   - Confirmation dialog: "X students unmarked — they will be marked absent"

---

#### [NEW] [route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/teacher/attendance/[assignmentId]/session/route.ts)

Controls for the session lifecycle:

- [PATCH](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/students/%5Bid%5D/fees/route.ts#116-187) — Update session status ([open](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/layout/PublicNavbar.tsx#214-218) → `reviewing` → `finalized`), toggle self-mark, set deadline
- [GET](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/teacher/marks/%5BassignmentId%5D/route.ts#10-64) — Fetch current session status + live counts (how many students have self-marked)

---

### Admin Attendance View

#### [NEW] [page.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/(admin)/admin/attendance/page.tsx)

Replaces the unused [AttendanceManager](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/admin/AttendanceManager.tsx#12-297) component with a proper admin page.

**Layout:**
1. **Filter Bar** — Date picker, Subject dropdown, Section dropdown, Batch dropdown
2. **Stats Row** — Total classes today, % marked, % finalized
3. **Records Table** — Each row shows: Student, Subject, Date, Status, Marked By, Lock status
   - Edited records show a small "✏️ Admin edited" badge
   - Edit button opens a modal with status dropdown + mandatory reason field
4. **Bulk Actions** — Lock/Unlock selected + Export CSV

Uses the existing server actions ([getAttendance](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/actions/attendance.ts#8-67), [updateStudentAttendance](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/actions/attendance.ts#115-135), [lockAttendance](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/actions/attendance.ts#136-149)) with the `marked_by: 'admin'` field populated on edits.

---

## UX States

| State | Visual | Teacher Action | Student Action |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Loading** | Skeleton shimmer cards | — | — |
| **Open** | 🟢 Green badge, live counters | Mark students, toggle self-mark | Self-mark if enabled |
| **Reviewing** | 🟡 Yellow badge | Fill gaps, review self-marks | View-only |
| **Finalized** | ⬜ Gray badge, lock icon | Read-only | View-only |
| **Low Attendance** | Red pulse on percentage | — | Warning banner |
| **No Classes** | Empty state with calendar icon | — | "No classes today" |

